name: A Store Room
description:
You are in a small dark store room.  A few common items are stacked
upon the shelves here, but very little looks interesting.

exits.keywords: door wooden~ 1 -1 2574 S #2576 A Bend In The Hallway~    You are at a bend in the long hallway.  The walls emit a faint magical glow which provides enough light to see by.    The hallway continues south and east from here.
